sentences.english: It has multiple regions that include dozens if not hundreds of branches.

sentences.english: The main rotary shaft can be simultaneously fixed with a plurality of circular discs with self rotation shafts.
sentences.chinese: 主轉軸上可同時固定多個帶自轉軸的圓盤。

sentences.english: You can select and move multiple artifacts in this manner.
sentences.chinese: 您可以按照這種方式選擇並移動多個工件。

sentences.chinese: 公司自主研發的產品已出口到150多個國家和地區。

sentences.english: So an ABR by definition is a member of two or more areas.

sentences.english: At present, Otis is operating in more than 200 ries and regions.

sentences.english: You can also combine multiple transformation animations in the same element.
sentences.chinese: 還可以在同一個元素中組合多個轉換動畫。

sentences.english: More than 550 priests were on hand to distribute  communion to the participants.

sentences.english: The cardboard box is provided with a plurality of hatches and a rift. The rift is connected with the hatch.
